Name: A Song's True Theme (I)
Desc: At the start of every wave of Cycle, summon 1 Trotter onto the field. The Trotter will be immediately defeated when it is Weakness Broken.\nAfter the Trotter is defeated, Advance the attacker's Action Forward by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color>, then apply Memory Imprint to all allies. Every stack of Memory Imprint increases the target's ATK by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#5[i]%</unbreak></color> and Break Effect by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak></color>, up to a max of <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak></color> stack(s).

Challenge.Name: Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Have no downed characters
